{"ts": "2026-04-11T20:59:59.050005+00:00", "event": "stream", "session_id": "chat_1775941182806_wk0wv", "query": "kahani suno", "corrected_query": "kahani suno", "model": "llama-3.3-70b-versatile", "role_mode": "assistant", "prompt_template": "default", "route": "direct", "route_reason": "general knowledge request", "route_confidence": 1.0, "route_source": "llm", "used_rag": false, "corrected": true, "citations": 0, "retrieved_documents": [], "retrieval": {"matches": 0, "hybrid_search": true, "context_chars": 0, "top_score": 0.0}, "response": "Ek kahani sunane ke liye, main aapko ek dilchasp yatra par le jaunga. Yeh kahani hai ek chhote se gaon ki, jahan ek ladka rehta tha jiska naam tha Rohan. Rohan ek bahut hi utsahit aur sakriya ladka tha, jo hamesha apne gaon ke baare mein jaanna chahta tha.\n\nRohan ne ek din socha ki woh apne gaon ke baare mein adhik jaanne ke liye ek yatra par niklega. Usne apne bag mein kuch zaruri cheezein pack ki, jaise ki khana, pani, aur ek map, aur phir woh apne safar par nikal pada. Usne apne gaon ke alag-alag hisson ko dekha, jaise ki khete, jungle, aur nadi, aur har jagah par usne naye logon se milne ka mauka paya.\n\nRohan ki yatra bahut hi romanchak thi, aur usne bahut kuch seekha. Usne apne gaon ke logon ki zarooraton ko samjha, aur usne dekha ki kaise woh apne gaon ko aur bhi accha bana sakta hai. Rohan ki kahani humein sikhati hai ki naye cheezein seekhne aur apne aas-paas ke logon ko samajhne ke liye, humein hamesha taiyar rehna chahiye.", "latency_ms": 3021.04}
