{"ts": "2026-04-11T21:00:32.769515+00:00", "event": "stream", "session_id": "chat_1775941182806_wk0wv", "query": "love story in hindi 5000 words sunao", "corrected_query": null, "model": "llama-3.3-70b-versatile", "role_mode": "assistant", "prompt_template": "default", "route": "direct", "route_reason": "general knowledge request", "route_confidence": 1.0, "route_source": "llm", "used_rag": false, "corrected": false, "citations": 0, "retrieved_documents": [], "retrieval": {"matches": 0, "hybrid_search": true, "context_chars": 0, "top_score": 0.0}, "response": "Ek sachchi love story sunane ke liye, main aapko ek kahani batata hoon. Yeh kahani hai Rohan aur Priya ki, jo ek dusre se college mein mile the. Rohan ek handsome aur intelligent ladka tha, jabki Priya ek sundar aur talented ladki thi. Unhone pehli baar ek college festival mein dekha tha, aur tab se unke beech ek ajeeb si connection ban gayi thi.\n\nRohan ne Priya ko impress karne ke liye kai tarah ki koshish ki, lekin Priya ne use pehli baar mein reject kar diya tha. Lekin Rohan ne himmat nahi haari aur use phir se try kiya. Is baar, Priya ne use apne dil ki baat batayi aur unhone ek dusre ko samjhne ki koshish ki. Unke beech ki baat-cheet badhti gayi aur ve ek dusre ke saath comfortable mehsoos karne lage.\n\nUnke rishte ne dhire-dhire badhna shuru kiya, aur ve ek dusre ke saath har pal bitane lage. Rohan ne Priya ko apne parivaar se milvaya, aur Priya ne Rohan ko apne doston se milvaya. Unke beech ki mohabbat badhti gayi, aur ve ek dusre ke bina reh nahi paate the. Lekin unke rishte mein bhi kuch utar-chadhav aaye, jaise ki unke parivaar ke beech ki ladai aur unke doston ke beech ki narazgi.\n\nUnhone in sabhi samasyaon ka samna kiya aur ek dusre ke saath khada raha. Unke beech ki mohabbat ne unhein ek dusre ke saath jodne ki takat di, aur ve ek dusre ke bina reh nahi paate the. Yeh kahani hai ek sachchi love story ki, jo humein sikhati hai ki mohabbat mein koi bhi samasya aaye, lekin agar hum ek dusre ke saath khade rahen, to hum kisi bhi mushkil ko paar kar sakte hain.", "latency_ms": 3158.07}
