{"ts": "2026-04-27T04:19:50.765008+00:00", "event": "stream", "user_id": "43489bbd9cf64a9c923017db8a244011", "session_id": "chat_1777235899364_ip58n", "query": "mujhe btao namaste ko tamil mein kya khte hai", "corrected_query": null, "model": "llama-3.3-70b-versatile", "role_mode": "assistant", "prompt_template": "generate_prompt", "route": "direct", "route_reason": "Default direct route.", "route_confidence": 0.64, "route_source": "heuristic", "fallback": false, "used_rag": false, "cache_hit": false, "corrected": false, "citations": 0, "retrieved_documents": [], "retrieval": {"matches": 0, "hybrid_search": true, "context_chars": 0, "top_score": 0.0}, "response": "# \ud83d\ude4f Main Heading\nNamaste ko Tamil mein \"Vanakkam\" kehte hai. Yeh ek aam abhivaadan hai jo Tamil bhaasha mein upyog kiya jaata hai.\n\n## \ud83d\udd39 Key Details\n* \"Vanakkam\" ka arth hota hai \"aadarpoorn abhivaadan\" ya \"namaskar\".\n* Yeh shabd Tamil bhaasha mein bahut aam hai aur log iska upyog karke ek dusre ko pranaam karte hain.\n\n## \ud83d\udea7 Issues / Challenges\n* Kabhi-kabhi log \"Vanakkam\" ko \"Namaste\" ke saath galat tareeke se upyog karte hain, jo ki dono bhaashao mein alag-alag abhivaadan hain.\n\n## \ud83c\udfaf Summary\n* Namaste ko Tamil mein \"Vanakkam\" kehte hai.\n* \"Vanakkam\" ka arth hota hai \"aadarpoorn abhivaadan\" ya \"namaskar\".\n* Yeh shabd Tamil bhaasha mein bahut aam hai aur log iska upyog karke ek dusre ko pranaam karte hain.", "latency_ms": 2118.07}
