5): Featured a 12-inch Retina display, up to 10 hours of battery life, and a starting price of around $1,300.\n\n## \ud83d\udcca Comparison\nHere's a brief comparison of the latest MacBook models:\n| Model | Display Size | Battery Life | Starting Price |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| MacBook Air | 13.3 inches | Up to 16 hours | Around $1,000 |\n| MacBook Pro | 13.3 or 16 inches | Up to 10 hours | Around $1,300 |\n\n## \ud83d\udea7 Issues\nSome common issues with MacBooks include:\n* Limited ports and connectivity options\n* High price point compared to other laptops\n* Limited upgrade and repair options\n\n## \ud83c\udfaf Summary\nIn summary, the MacBook series offers a range of laptop options with unique features and capabilities, including:\n* Thin and lightweight designs\n* Advanced performance and functionality\n* High-quality Retina displays\n* Long battery life\n* Limited ports and connectivity options\n* High price point compared to other laptops", "latency_ms": 2695.69}
